{"tid":257551,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"急 誠招絲打夾租","createTime":"2017-05-25T11:06:16.000Z","updateTime":"2017-07-31T14:44:10.000Z","uid":118655,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"ec27637ed1efbd6c34b70ef9a971bdadc1021467","tid":257551,"uid":118655,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-25T11:06:16.000Z","msg":"首選九龍區，次選沙田，三選港島區<br />\n<br />\n本身睇中翔龍灣一個兩房單位，新淨，向海，有露台，單住裡面有齊晒所有家電梳化餐台床同衣櫃，基本上買套床單就住得。但業主開價一萬六千幾，而且有大細房之分，諗住自己住大房，所以自己出1萬，細房就收6-7千。<br />\n<br />\n當然啦，如果嫌貴嘅，可以一齊去搵其他區同盤，如果兩間房大細差唔多就一日一半租金，其餘水電煤上網費就一日一半。<br />\n<br />\n我自己乾淨，唔嘈，唔煙唔酒唔蒲，早上返工晚上返學，會煮飯帶飯返工，就得人，唔港女，唔太計較，希望搵一個唔煙唔酒既女仔一齊夾租。"},{"pid":"2071d8a052e8dbe65b1b03e5d7b87ade725b77af","tid":257551,"uid":118655,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-25T11:07:49.000Z","msg":"有意tg wongwong99"},{"pid":"b75050d0730bdbae1049223570397b26d726dbd8","tid":257551,"uid":45148,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-25T11:09:02.000Z","msg":"靚唔靚仔先<br />\n毒柒 乾淨都無用"},{"pid":"0b313699b323f09fe70bd8561251b35fc942ac53","tid":257551,"uid":20227,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-25T11:09:15.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"2395a0b9bc856f874f1f40cbcddb53256df3c6d1","tid":257551,"uid":118655,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-25T11:13:33.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>靚唔靚仔先<br />\n毒柒 乾淨都無用</blockquote><br />\n要絲打呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0d1ebf114a43d982d01fc293ddcba325d9a39962","tid":257551,"uid":118655,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-25T11:13:48.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>太貴</blockquote>私樓 靚盤"},{"pid":"4bd26af4fb1d583222c2dbd76ba11a57fe3aead1","tid":257551,"uid":118655,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-25T11:26:22.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1264e6d993ae6f556d9d917b0e0f8be06d938fb4","tid":257551,"uid":91664,"like":0,"disl